This paper deals with natural language to SQL task, which involves natural language processing, database querying, and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses parsing techniques and models, which are related to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Learning). The use of oracles and accuracy evaluation are related to cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.DB (Databases).
